vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting an MF-1(A) Multifamily District on property zoned CR Community Retail District, on the northwest line of Paducah Avenue, between South Denley Drive and South Lancaster Road
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval
